tps://blog.csdn.net/amorcyc/article/details/105506315", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "非结构化数据", "mastery_score": 50.0, "priority": 6, "llm_priority": 7, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "非结构化数据到底应该如何管理？", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1aZ4y1q7ZR", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>结构化数据</em>、半<em>结构化数据</em>和<em>非结构化数据</em>分析", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45847421/article/details/115499725", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "结构化数据", "mastery_score": 54.0, "priority": 7, "llm_priority": 6, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "【打工人必会技能】从纯文本到结构化数据", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Lz4y1z7oE", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>结构化数据</em>、半<em>结构化数据</em>和非<em>结构化数据</em>分析", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45847421/article/details/115499725", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "大数据生命周期", "mastery_score": 54.38, "priority": 8, "llm_priority": 8, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "黑马程序员大数据入门到实战教程，大数据开发必会的Hadoop、Hive，云平台实战项目全套一网打尽", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1WY4y197g7", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "数据质量在<em>大数据生命周期</em>中的关键作用与保障方法", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/2301_76268839/article/details/150701633", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "DIKW金字塔模型", "mastery_score": 58.71, "priority": 9, "llm_priority": 9, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "PPT改稿-神奇的DIKW金字塔模型", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1PF4m1A7FP", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "什么是<em>DIKW金字塔模型</em>？", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/godlovedaniel/article/details/154023964", "source": "csdn"}]}], "llm_advice": "按照上述顺序学习更合理，因为数据管理过程是基础，HDFS数据操作依赖于对数据管理的理解，Spark架构和数据清洗则建立在HDFS操作之上，而数据集成和结构化数据处理则需要更高级的知识整合。针对数据管理过程，你可以先从数据存储和管理的基本概念开始，通过阅读相关书籍和在线教程；对于Spark架构，可以先观看官方文档和教程视频，逐步理解其工作原理。加油，我相信你一定可以掌握这些知识！", "llm_order_reason": "基于知识点的依赖关系和复杂度逐步递增"}','2026-04-05T15:32:12.842856');
