/amorcyc/article/details/105506315", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "结构化数据", "mastery_score": 54.0, "priority": 6, "llm_priority": 2, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "【打工人必会技能】从纯文本到结构化数据", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Lz4y1z7oE", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>结构化数据</em>、半<em>结构化数据</em>和非<em>结构化数据</em>分析", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45847421/article/details/115499725", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "非结构化数据", "mastery_score": 58.0, "priority": 7, "llm_priority": 3, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "非结构化数据到底应该如何管理？", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1aZ4y1q7ZR", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>结构化数据</em>、半<em>结构化数据</em>和<em>非结构化数据</em>分析", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45847421/article/details/115499725", "source": "csdn"}]}], "llm_advice": "建议从数据管理过程开始，理解数据生命周期和基础概念，再逐步学习结构化与非结构化数据处理，为数据集成打下基础。掌握HDFS数据操作后，能更好地处理分布式存储，再学习数据清洗提升数据质量。这样由浅入深，逐步构建完整知识体系。对于数据管理过程，建议先阅读教材梳理流程；HDFS操作可结合实践项目加深理解。加油，你已经走在大数据学习的正确道路上！", "llm_order_reason": "从基础概念到技术实现，逐步构建大数据处理的知识体系。"}','2026-04-05T16:09:16.118910');
INSERT INTO "learning_plans" VALUES('stuwangqiyu','stuwangqiyu_plan_20251226_143354.json','data\user_data\stuwangqiyu\learning_plans\stuwangqiyu_plan_20251226_143354.json','user','[{"date": "2025-12-26", "priority": "基础知识", "topic": "了解机器学习", "materials": ["当然，以下是一个简明的高质量推荐列表，帮助人们学习“了解机器学习”：", "### 中文资源", "1. **《机器学习》（周志华）**", "   - 简介：这本书是机器学习领域的经典教材，适合初学者和进阶学习者。内容涵盖了监督学习、无监督学习、强化学习等各个方面。", "   - 出版社：清华大学出版社", "2. **《统计学习方法》（李航）**", "   - 简介：李航老师的这本书详细介绍了各种统计学习方法，适合有一定基础的读者。", "   - 出版社：清华大学出版社", "3. **《机器学习实战》（Peter Harrington）**", "   - 简介：通过实际案例和代码，帮助读者理解和应用机器学习算法。", "   - 出版社：人民邮电出版社", "### 英文资源", "1. **\"Pattern Recognition and Machine Learning\" by Christopher M. Bishop**", "   - 简介：这本书是机器学习领域的经典教材，内容深入，适合有一定基础的读者。", "   - 出版社：Springer", "2. **\"Machine Learning: A Probabilistic Perspective\" by Kevin P. Murphy**", "   - 简介：从概率视角介绍机器学习，内容广泛且深入。", "   - 出版社：MIT Press", "3. **\"Deep Learning\" by Ian Goodfellow, Yoshua Bengio, and Aaron Courville**", "   - 简介：这本书全面介绍了深度学习的理论和实践，是深度学习领域的权威教材。", "   - 出版社：MIT Press", "### 在线资源", "1. **Coursera - Machine Learning by Andrew Ng**", "   - 简介：Andrew Ng教授的机器学习课程，适合初学者，内容涵盖基础理论和实际应用。", "   - 链接：[Coursera Machine Learning](https://www.coursera.org/learn/machine-learning)", "2. **edX - Introduction to Machine Learning with Python by University of Washington**", "   - 简介：通过Python介绍机器学习的基本概念和方法，适合初学者。", "   - 链接：[edX Machine Learning with Python](https://www.edx.org/course/introduction-to-machine-learning-with-python)", "3. **吴恩达的个人博客**", "   - 简介：Andrew Ng的博客中有很多关于机器学习的文章和教程，内容丰富且易于理解。", "   - 链接：[Andrew Ng''s Blog](https://www.coursera.org/blog)", "希望这些资源能帮助您更好地学习机器学习！"], "deadline": "2026-01-02"}]','2026-04-05T16:09:16.128846');
INSERT INTO "learning_plans" VALUES('zyh','zyh_plan_20251216_233157.json','data\user_data\zyh\learning_plans\zyh_plan_20251216_233157.json','user','[{"date": "2025-12-16", "priority": "基础知识", "topic": "学习数据挖掘", "materials": ["当然，以下是推荐的学习数据挖掘的资源列表，包括中文和英文材料：", "### 中文资源", "1. **《数据挖掘导论》**（Introduction to Data Mining） - 作者：Jiawei Han, Micheline Kamber, Jian Pei", "   - 简介：这本书是数据挖掘领域的经典教材，适合初学者和进阶学习者。", "2. **《数据科学：从入门到精通》**（Data Science from Scratch to Finish） - 作者：Joel Grus", "   - 简介：虽然这本书是用英文写的，但其中很多概念和数据科学的基础知识同样适用于中文读者。", "3. **《Python数据挖掘手册》**（Python Data Mining Handbook） - 作者：Udaya K. Koduri", "   - 简介：这本书详细介绍了使用Python进行数据挖掘的各种技术和方法。", "### 英文资源", "1. **《Data Mining: Concepts and Techniques》**（数据挖掘：概念与技术） - 作者：Jiawei Han, Micheline Kamber, Jian Pei", "   - 简介：这是数据挖掘领域的权威教材，涵盖了基本概念、算法和技术。", "2. **《Introduction to Data Mining》**（数据挖掘简介） - 作者：Charu C. Aggarwal", "   - 简介：这本书提供了数据挖掘的全面介绍，适合初学者。", "3. **《Machine Learning Yearning》** - 作者：Andrew Ng", "   - 简介：虽然不是专门针对数据挖掘，但这本书提供了很多关于机器学习和数据挖掘的实用建议和技巧。", "4. **KDnuggets** - 网站", "   - 简介：KDnuggets 是一个提供数据科学、机器学习和数据挖掘最新资讯和教程的网站。", "5. **Coursera - Data Mining Specialization** - 由 University of Washington 提供", "   - 简介：这个专项课程涵盖了数据挖掘的各个方面，包括基础、算法和应用。", "### 在线课程", "1. **Coursera - Data Mining and Machine Learning** - 由 University of Washington 提供", "   - 简介：涵盖数据挖掘和机器学习的基础知识，适合初学者。", "2. **edX - Data Science MicroMasters** - 由 University of California, Berkeley 提供", "   - 简介：这是一个系列课程，涵盖了数据科学的多个方面，包括数据挖掘。", "### 博客和文章", "1. **Towards Data Science** - 博客", "   - 简介：这是一个高质量的数据科学博客，包含大量关于数据挖掘的文章和教程。", "2. **KDNuggets** - 文章集合", "   - 简介：KDNuggets 提供了大量关于数据挖掘和机器学习的文章和教程。", "### 视频资源", "1. **YouTube - Data Mining Tutorials**", "   - 简介：在YouTube上搜索“数据挖掘教程”，可以找到很多相关的教学视频。", "2. **Coursera - Video Lectures**", "   - 简介：Coursera上的数据挖掘课程通常包含详细的视频讲座，适合系统学习。", "希望这些资源能帮助您更好地学习数据挖掘！"], "deadline": "2026-01-15"}]','2026-04-05T16:09:16.138778');
INSERT INTO "learning_plans" VALUES('zyh','zyh_path_20260405_165748.json','','path','{"username": "zyh", "generated_at": "2026-04-05T16:57:48.826928", "status": "active", "weak_nodes": [{"node_id": "数据管理过程", "mastery_score": 29.0, "priority": 1, "llm_priority": 1, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "【南京大学】数据管理基础", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1S7411M7pu", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>数据管理</em>基础知识", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/qq_33840251/article/details/132093448", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "HDFS数据操作", "mastery_score": 34.5, "priority": 2, "llm_priority": 5, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "实验2 HDFS基本操作", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1kwE7zSEhr", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>HDFS</em>-<em>操作</em>", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/2403_88719012/article/details/143508208", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "数据清洗", "mastery_score": 40.0, "priority": 3, "llm_priority": 6, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "【Python 数据清洗】用Python给数据洗澡澡~ |数据分析|数据清洗|数据预处理|", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1qb411M7ew", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "spark<em>数据清洗教程</em>", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/2401_87250241/article/details/146949421", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "Spark架构", "mastery_score": 47.0, "priority": 4, "llm_priority": 7, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "03_Spark架构原理", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1yv4y1S72s", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>Spark</em>入门<em>教程</em>", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/2501_90817125/article/details/148559524", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "数据集成", "mastery_score": 47.5, "priority": 5, "llm_priority": 4, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "14.数据集成", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1UJ4m1H7Xi", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>数据</em>分析实战45讲（12） <em>数据集成</em>", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/amorcyc/article/details/105506315", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "结构化数据", "mastery_score": 54.0, "priority": 6, "llm_priority": 2, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "OnekeyComp-Comp2结构化数据建模", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Eb421i7nn", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>结构化数据</em>、半<em>结构化数据</em>和非<em>结构化数据</em>分析", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45847421/article/details/115499725", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "非结构化数据", "mastery_score": 58.0, "priority": 7, "llm_priority": 3, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "非结构化数据到底应该如何管理？", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1aZ4y1q7ZR", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>结构化数据</em>、半<em>结构化数据</em>和<em>非结构化数据</em>分析", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45847421/article/details/115499725", "source": "csdn"}]}], "llm_advice": "学习顺序合理：数据管理是基础框架，先掌握整体流程；结构化/非结构化数据类型为数据集成提供认知基础；数据集成需依赖数据类型处理逻辑；HDFS作为存储层需在集成后学习；数据清洗需基于存储数据预处理；Spark架构作为处理引擎需在清洗后掌握。建议：1. 数据管理过程优先梳理数据生命周期与元数据管理，结合案例理解各阶段任务；2. HDFS操作重点掌握分布式存储原理与基础命令，通过搭建集群实践加深理解。坚持按此顺序学习，逐步夯实基础，你一定能掌握大数据核心技能！", "llm_order_reason": "数据管理过程是基础框架，需先理解整体流程；数据类型（结构化/非结构化）为数据集成提供基础认知；数据集成依赖数据类型处理逻辑；HDFS作为存储层需在数据集成后学习；数据清洗需基于存储后的数据进行预处理；Spark架构作为处理引擎需在数据清洗后掌握以实现数据分析。"}','2026-04-05T16:57:48.828267');
INSERT INTO "learning_plans" VALUES('zyh','zyh_path_20260405_170339.json','','path','{"username": "zyh", "generated_at": "2026-04-05T17:03:39.985260", "status": "active", "weak_nodes": [{"node_id": "数据管理过程", "mastery_score": 29.0, "priority": 1, "llm_priority": 1, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "【南京大学】数据管理基础", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1S7411M7pu", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>数据管理</em>基础知识", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/qq_33840251/article/details/132093448", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "HDFS数据操作", "mastery_score": 34.5, "priority": 2, "llm_priority": 5, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "实验2 HDFS基本操作", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1kwE7zSEhr", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>HDFS</em>-<em>操作</em>", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/2403_88719012/article/details/143508208", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "数据清洗", "mastery_score": 40.0, "priority": 3, "llm_priority": 6, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "【Python 数据清洗】用Python给数据洗澡澡~ |数据分析|数据清洗|数据预处理|", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1qb411M7ew", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "spark<em>数据清洗教程</em>", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/2401_87250241/article/details/146949421", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "Spark架构", "mastery_score": 47.0, "priority": 4, "llm_priority": 7, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "03_Spark架构原理", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1yv4y1S72s", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>Spark</em>入门<em>教程</em>", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/2501_90817125/article/details/148559524", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "数据集成", "mastery_score": 47.5, "priority": 5, "llm_priority": 4, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "14.数据集成", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1UJ4m1H7Xi", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>数据</em>分析实战45讲（12） <em>数据集成</em>", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/amorcyc/article/details/105506315", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "结构化数据", "mastery_score": 54.0, "priority": 6, "llm_priority": 2, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "OnekeyComp-Comp2结构化数据建模", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Eb421i7nn", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>结构化数据</em>、半<em>结构化数据</em>和非<em>结构化数据</em>分析", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45847421/article/details/115499725", "source": "csdn"}]}, {"node_id": "非结构化数据", "mastery_score": 58.0, "priority": 7, "llm_priority": 3, "resources": [{"type": "video", "title": "非结构化数据到底应该如何管理？", "url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1aZ4y1q7ZR", "source": "bilibili"}, {"type": "blog", "title": "<em>结构化数据</em>、半<em>结构化数据</em>和<em>非结构化数据</em>分析", "url": "https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45847421/article/details/115499725", "source": "csdn"}]}], "llm_advice": "建议先学习数据管理过程，建立大数据处理的整体框架认知。掌握结构化与非结构化数据类型后，能更好理解数据集成的必要性，为HDFS存储操作奠定基础。数据清洗需在数据集成后进行，确保数据质量后再学习Spark架构，能更清晰理解其处理场景。针对数据管理过程，建议系统学习《大数据管理》教材并完成企业级数据流程模拟项目；数据清洗可从Kaggle数据集入手，每天练习1小时数据预处理任务。坚持即可突破瓶颈，加油！", "llm_order_reason": "数据管理过程作为基础框架，需先掌握整体流程；结构化与非结构化数据是数据类型的基础认知；数据集成依赖数据类型理解；HDFS数据操作是数据存储的核心技术；数据清洗需在数据集成后进行；Spark架构作为处理框架，需在数据清洗后学习以理解其应用场景。"}','2026-04-05T17:03:39.986580');
